org.apache.manifoldcf.crawler

Class RunSimpleHistory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.manifoldcf.crawler.RunSimpleHistory

  • public class RunSimpleHistory
extends Object
    This class converts a job name into a job identifier. Warning: Since multiple jobs can have the same name, a list of job identifiers will be returned.
